<paragraph blockId="8.[189,1399,1019,1080]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
The name is derived from the Latinized name of the 
<typeStatus box="[814,865,1019,1045]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">type</typeStatus>
locality (the island of Öland, 
<collectingCountry box="[1220,1315,1019,1045]" name="Sweden" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Sweden</collectingCountry>
) of the species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
